Airline names

Source: R/airlines.R
airlines.Rd

Look up airline names from their carrier codes.

Usage

airlines

Format

Data frame with columns

carrier

Two letter abbreviation.

name

Full name.

Source

https://www.transtats.bts.gov/DL_SelectFields.aspx?gnoyr_VQ=FGJ&QO_fu146_anzr=b0-gvzr

Examples

airlines
#> # A tibble: 14 × 2
#>    carrier name                              
#>    <chr>   <chr>                             
#>  1 9E      Endeavor Air Inc.                 
#>  2 AA      American Airlines Inc.            
#>  3 AS      Alaska Airlines Inc.              
#>  4 DL      Delta Air Lines Inc.              
#>  5 EV      ExpressJet Airlines LLC d/b/a aha!
#>  6 F9      Frontier Airlines Inc.            
#>  7 FL      AirTran Airways Corporation       
#>  8 MQ      Envoy Air                         
#>  9 NK      Spirit Air Lines                  
#> 10 OO      SkyWest Airlines Inc.             
#> 11 UA      United Air Lines Inc.             
#> 12 US      US Airways Inc.                   
#> 13 WN      Southwest Airlines Co.            
#> 14 YV      Mesa Airlines Inc.
